{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"5015","text":"God does not exist.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5016","text":"A better world cannot exist","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5017","text":"God cannot prefer a world without evil","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5018","text":"God exists.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5019","text":"If God is all powerful He can create any world that He wants.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5020","text":"If God is all good than He would create a world without evil.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5021","text":"Therefore evil should not exis","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5022","text":"evil does exist.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5023","text":"Dr. Curley would have to show that there is a world of free creatures which God could create which has as much good as this world but which has less evil.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5024","text":"how could he possibly prove such a thing?  It is pure speculation.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5025","text":"If God wills to create free creatures then it's logically impossible for Him to make them freely do what He wants.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5026","text":"If he wants to reject the claim he has to consider the relation between the free will and the evil","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:26"},{"nodeID":"5027","text":"Dr. Curley would have to prove that there is another world that God could have created with this much knowledge of God and His salvation but with less evils.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5028","text":"But how could anyone prove such a thing?  Again it is pure speculation.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5029","text":"that premise might be true if God's purpose were to create a comfortable environment for His human pets.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5030","text":"on the Christian view we are not God's pets","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5031","text":"the purpose of life is not happiness as such but rather the knowledge of God and His salvation  which will ultimately bring true happiness","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5032","text":"many evils occur in life which are utterly pointless with respect to producing human happiness.  But they may not be pointless with respect to producing a deeper knowledge of God.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5033","text":"If he wants to reject the claim he has to consider the relation between evil and salvation","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5034","text":"CA","type":"CA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5035","text":"CA","type":"CA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27"},{"nodeID":"5036","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:27","scheme":"CauseToEffect","schemeID":"4"},{"nodeID":"5037","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:28"},{"nodeID":"5038","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:28","scheme":"PracticalReasoning","schemeID":"28"},{"nodeID":"5039","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:29"},{"nodeID":"5040","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:34:29","scheme":"PracticalReasoning","schemeID":"28"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"4707","fromID":"5016","toID":"5034","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4708","fromID":"5034","toID":"5019","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4709","fromID":"5017","toID":"5035","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4710","fromID":"5035","toID":"5020","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4711","fromID":"5018","toID":"5036","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4712","fromID":"5019","toID":"5036","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4713","fromID":"5020","toID":"5036","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4714","fromID":"5021","toID":"5036","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4715","fromID":"5022","toID":"5036","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4716","fromID":"5036","toID":"5015","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4717","fromID":"5023","toID":"5037","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4718","fromID":"5024","toID":"5037","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4719","fromID":"5037","toID":"5016","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4720","fromID":"5025","toID":"5038","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4721","fromID":"5026","toID":"5038","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4722","fromID":"5038","toID":"5023","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4723","fromID":"5027","toID":"5039","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4724","fromID":"5028","toID":"5039","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4725","fromID":"5039","toID":"5017","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4726","fromID":"5029","toID":"5040","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4727","fromID":"5030","toID":"5040","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4728","fromID":"5031","toID":"5040","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4729","fromID":"5032","toID":"5040","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4730","fromID":"5033","toID":"5040","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"4731","fromID":"5040","toID":"5027","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}